{"tid":2180780,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[有片] 有手足作左首歌送比羅冠聰同埋一眾流亡海外手足","createTime":"2020-08-30T06:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T06:53:55.000Z","uid":279513,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f4654de7dd3097a83c16e820beb7dc4a60ff3116","tid":2180780,"uid":279513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T06:29:08.000Z","msg":"利申借朋友account<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首歌名叫 竹木日水廿金山<br />\n係咪好撚怪呢? 明顯係倉頡撚<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=srPmq6snVkc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsrPmq6snVkc&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLLtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=da7e2d3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=srPmq6snVkc</a><br />\n<br />\n素人黎講唱歌都只係一般, 但誠意搭夠<br />\n睇埋歌詞, 作者可能係利迷黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但都係講離開左香港幾耐都好, 都好掛住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n水廿金山，水廿金山<br />\n你美麗獨特不凡<br />\n水廿金山，水廿金山<br />\n你令世界驚嘆<br />\n<br />\n水裡霓虹艷光閃<br />\n廿年後卻大大改變<br />\n金色的年華，已漸化煙<br />\n山卻像獅子，令我立志堅<br />\n<br />\n竹木日水廿金山，竹木日水廿金山<br />\n你永遠無懼艱難<br />\n竹木日水廿金山，竹木日水廿金山<br />\n你永遠不會孤單<br />\n<br />\n水令你我能夠相逢<br />\n廿年內卻不斷走相送<br />\n金光不再燦爛，憤怒在我心中<br />\n山卻在高處，讓我踏上天空<br />\nYou'll never walk alone<br />\n<br />\n竹木日水廿金山，竹木日水廿金山<br />\n你永遠無懼艱難<br />\n竹木日水廿金山，竹木日水廿金山<br />\n你永遠不會孤單<br />\n<br />\n我愛你的心，永遠不冷<br />\n<br />\n鐘意可以like埋嗰位手足個page<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cisum1music\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcisum1music&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLLtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=38ac940c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cisum1music</a>"},{"pid":"813f33fdc16019650268a47ac265f1c3198fe999","tid":2180780,"uid":279513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30